OL,3,CMet Office warns of rise in extreme UK
OL,4,Cweather, as 2023 second hottest year
OL,5,Cever
OL,7,FOur weather is becoming more extreme
OL,8,Fmore often, according to the Met
OL,9,FOffice's State of Climate report.
OL,11,FIt compares weather data and events
OL,12,Ffrom last year with statistics dating
OL,13,Fback to the 19th century.
OL,15,FThe headline figure is that 2023 was
OL,16,Fthe second hottest year on record for
OL,17,Fthe UK as a whole, and the hottest
OL,18,Fever for Wales and Northern Ireland.
