OL,5,Cever
OL,7,FBut in 2023, that rose to 20 days
OL,8,Facross 11 different counties in the
OL,9,Fsouth and east of England.
OL,11,FThe number of "extremely wet" days was
OL,12,F20% higher in the most recent decade
OL,13,Fthan in the 60s, 70s and 80s.
OL,15,FMarch, July, October and December 2023
OL,16,Fwere all in the UK's top-ten wettest
OL,17,Fmonths ever, according to records
OL,18,Fwhich go back to 1836.
