OL,12,FProfessor Liz Bentley, Chief Executive
OL,13,Fof the Royal Meteorological Society
OL,14,Fsaid: "The new analysis of days that
OL,15,Fare classified as 'hot' or having
OL,16,F'exceptional rainfall' highlights the
OL,17,Fincreased frequency in high impact
OL,18,Fextremes we are already experiencing
OL,19,Fin the UK.
